    "description": {
      "value": "<div><p>Flame-like shadows wreathe your body until the spell ends, causing you to become heavily obscured to others. The shadows turn dim light within 10 feet of you into darkness, and bright light in the same area to dim light.</p><p>Until the spell ends, you have resistance to radiant damage. In addition, whenever a creature within a number of feet equal to 5 times your Proficiency Bonus of you hits you with an attack, or forces you to make a saving throw, the shadows lash out at that creature, dealing it 2d8 plus your spellcasting ability modifier necrotic damage.</p></div>",
